name: NO F#@%'s GIVEN Collar Necklace
description:
Yea yea so you usually only see these in XXX shops.. Get over it. They give any outfit that bit of edge you're looking for, whether rocking a vintage concert tee with skinny jeans or dressed totally cute in a sunflower dress. Buckle up!

The leather used to make this collar is Napa Hot-stuffed Latigo Leather. It is of excellent quality and has been dyed full through and treated with a variety of softeners for flexibility and bend making for a surprisingly very comfortable fit. 

The collar is ¾” wide and has a Plated ring in the front. The plate and D-ring are ¾" wide and the O-ring is 1" in diameter.  There is a buckle and eyelets in the back. All fittings are nickel-plated steel. 

Fits Neck Size 13”- 15½" (33-39cm). Pretty much one size fits all but please measure your neck first just in case.
